        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Simplifying Management, Reallocation, and Transfer of Spectrum Act or the SMART Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the National Telecommunications and Information Administration to implement a standardized framework that facilitates the sharing of electromagnetic spectrum between nonfederal users and federal entities.</p> <p>This framework must enable the secure management of harmful interference between nonfederal users and federal entities that share a spectrum band in order to ensure access by such nonfederal users to the spectrum band.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
